text: Ong Hock Eng (born 8 October 1933) is a Malaysian former sports shooter. He competed in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Malaysian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Malaya Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Selangor
